&lt;li&gt;PPT：见 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/cloudnativeto/academy/tree/master/meetup/14-dalian&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
